uniol.apt.adt.extension

Class Extensible

  • java.lang.Object
    • uniol.apt.adt.extension.Extensible
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExtensible
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractGraph, Edge, Node, SubEdge, SubGraph, SubNode

    public class Extensible
extends java.lang.Object
implements IExtensible
    The Extensible class describes an advanced object consisting of an id and a key \rightarrow value property mapping and for every object a flag is saved if the object should by copied (referenzcopy), if the owner object is copied.
    Author:
    Dennis-Michael Borde, Manuel Gieseking
